配合Apache使用
LoadModule php_module /usr/local/opt/php/lib/httpd/modules/libphp.so
<FilesMatch \.php$>
    SetHandler application/x-httpd-php
</FilesMatch>
DirectoryIndex index.php index.html
%
PHP默认配置php.ini、php-fpm.ini在/usr/local/etc/php/8.5/
%
后台服务：brew services start php
一次性：/usr/local/opt/php/sbin/php-fpm --nodaemonize